reviews.reviewText: I HAD to buy these because ALL of the ones I had just stopped working and kept making that ding sound literally EVERY 5 SECONDS and wouldn’t charge my phone, I had tried different wall outlets, different charging block plug in’s etc and nothing at all worked so it was 100% guaranteed the actual cords that I had which was a 4 pack and ALL of them started doing this…. Then I borrowed my mom’s cord and of course it worked PERFECTLY!!! Keep in mind I have “automatic updates” turned OFF so keeping that off has PROVEN that they still do push some kind of updates through somehow…. Anyways I bought these and they work perfectly and I’m definitely happy with the price as well!!! I HATE the fact that Apple does this on purpose with their little secret updates which cause the cords not to work so you have to BUY MORE!!! Super annoying and proves what kind of a company they are!!!
